              <div className="relative z-10 text-slate-700 text-[13px] leading-relaxed font-medium space-y-3">
                <p>
                  <strong className="text-indigo-900 font-bold">{minifig.item_no}</strong> is a delightfully dark figure from the LEGO Wednesday theme, launched in 2024 based on the hit Netflix series. This theme perfectly captures the gothic, deadpan aesthetic of Wednesday Addams and the colorful contrast of her Nevermore Academy peers.
                </p>
                <p>
                  These figures are highly sought after for their unique, moody torso prints, specialized hairpieces, and the inclusion of iconic elements like 'Thing'. Featured in sets like Wednesday Addams' Room (76781) and the Nevermore Academy (76786), they are essential for fans of the Addams Family universe and those looking to add a touch of macabre charm to their LEGO displays.
                </p>
              </div>
